Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This video\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1878}, {\"ngram\": \"a lawyer\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1915}, {\"ngram\": \"an undisclosed complainant\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1955}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'According to the information received, the footage was allegedly taken several years ago during a training session conducted by Ms. Dujardin at a private stable.\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the information\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1987}, {\"ngram\": \"the footage\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"a training session\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms. Dujardin\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"a private stable\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A video has emerged from four years ago which shows me making an error of judgement during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A video\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Understandably, the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI) is investigating and I have made the decision to withdraw from all competition - including the Paris Olympics - while this process takes place.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2302, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.867578608008434e-46, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"all competition\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"this process\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2497}, {\"ngram\": \"my horses\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"my pupils\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"no excuse\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better example\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sincerely sorry for my actions and devastated that I have let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2755, \"end\": 2762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9975867406838215, \"rank\": 0.0024190971968582925, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my actions\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2738}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will cooperate fully with the FEI, British Equestrian Federation and British Dressage during their investigations, and will not be commenting further until the process is complete.\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.867578608008434e-46, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2821, \"end\": 2850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2855, \"end\": 2871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their investigations\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Dujardin, 23rd July 2024\\u2032 'Upon receiving the video, the FEI promptly initiated an investigation.\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2968, \"end\": 2986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}, {\"begin\": 3036, \"end\": 3039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.867578608008434e-46, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"July 2024\\u2032\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3003}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3029}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As part of this investigation, Ms. Dujardin, British Equestrian, and British Dressage were informed of the allegations.\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3122, \"end\": 3140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"this investigation\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3106}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms. Dujardin\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"the allegations\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ms Dujardin was given a deadline of 17:00 Swiss time on 23 July to respond to the allegations.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3241, \"end\": 3246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.8700366786735787, \"rank\": 0.14937644053939914, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http